</line><line>Phoenix:
I-I see... <textEffects>(This pageant sure is...something.)</textEffects>
</line><line>Layton:
By the way...I just noticed something rather odd.
</line><line>Vigilante (Foxy):
And what's that?
</line><line>Layton:
